            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.1</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's New

- **Calendar Integration** — View Apple Calendar events alongside Nepali dates and export holidays to your calendar
- **Refined UI** — Smoother animations, redesigned event tabs, and subtler calendar grid
- **Design Overhaul** — Polished visuals across the calendar with improved typography and spacing
]]></description>
