            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's New

- **Desktop Widgets** — Nepali date and calendar widgets on your desktop (small & medium)
- **Event Countdown** — Widgets show days remaining for upcoming events
- **Collapsible Event Indicators** — Toggle event/holiday dots on the calendar
- **Sky Theme** — New Sky color scheme with gradient backgrounds
]]></description>
